des: "Super tasty for a breakfast, a quick snack, or even dessert. Great for those days were you can't seem to stop thinking about the ice cream in your freezer."
ins: Divide about 1/4 cup chopped peach into two small cups or bowls, followed by a layer of about 1/4 cup donuts. Spread about 1/2 of the yogurt over donuts, then repeat layers once more.
